CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 20, 1958 pg. A16 reads: "Wed At Home Of Bride - Mr. and Mrs. Raymond Porter were united in marriage at the home of the bride. She is the former Juanita McKinney, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. Bert McKinney.  He is the son of Mr. and Mrs. Walter Porter.  Margie Jackson and W.C. Horne were attendants. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Raymond Porter and Juanita McKinney Porter, posed cutting three tiered wedding cake, in home of Mr. and Mrs. Bert McKinney, possibly 238 Burrows Street, Oakland, another version
